message.text:
Hi OPC, 💚

Thank you so much for your support today! 🙏 To everyone who dropped by and bought food, we’re truly grateful. Hoping for another sold-out day tomorrow with the help of our amazing community. 🌟

📋 Tomorrow’s Menu
🍴 Chicken Parmigiana — ₱120
🍴 Chicken Curry Katsu — ₱130
🍴 General Tso’s Chicken — ₱110
🍴 Chicken Pastil — ₱50
🍴 Honey Glazed Pork Belly — ₱120
🍴 Pad Kra Pao (Thai Stir-Fried Minced Pork) — ₱110
🍴 Beef Salpicao — ₱145
🍴 Beef Stroganoff — ₱155
🌯 Creamy Spinach Mexican Wraps — ₱95

📍 Visit us at Munch Box Express
(Beside Bro Sisig and FEU FC Building – Feuture Center)

I also hope you understand and allow me to share our updates here. Your support means a lot, and together let’s make tomorrow another sold-out day! 💚✨
